 Family-style brunch, served from 10 a.m. to 2 p.m., includes starters like salad, shrimp cocktail and beignets. Choose breakfast (eggs, hash browns, bread pudding French toast and eggs Benedict) or lunch (beef brisket, glazed ham, vegetables, risotto, tortigiloni rossa) and, of course, dessert. Cost is $44.95 for adults, $14.95 for kids 12 and under. You've read your complimentary articles for this time period.
